* (2004) ''Tuma P<U+0101>vaka Ma<U+0310>ha Karahu Niv<U+0101>s<U+0101>'' (<U+0924><U+0941><U+092E> <U+092A><U+093E><U+0935><U+0915> <U+092E><U+0901><U+0939> <U+0915><U+0930><U+0939><U+0941> <U+0928><U+093F><U+0935><U+093E><U+0938><U+093E>)&nbsp;<U+2013> Hindi discourse.
* (2005) ''Bh<U+0101>v<U+0101>rthabodhin<U+012B>'' (<U+092D><U+093E><U+0935><U+093E><U+0930><U+094D><U+0925><U+092C><U+094B><U+0927><U+093F><U+0928><U+0940>)&nbsp;<U+2013> Hindi commentary on the Ramcharitmanas.
* (2007) ''<U+015A>r<U+012B>r<U+0101>sapa<U+00F1>c<U+0101>dhy<U+0101>y<U+012B>vimar<U+015B>a<U+1E25>'' (<U+0936><U+094D><U+0930><U+0940><U+0930><U+093E><U+0938><U+092A><U+091E><U+094D><U+091A><U+093E><U+0927><U+094D><U+092F><U+093E><U+092F><U+0940><U+0935><U+093F><U+092E><U+0930><U+094D><U+0936><U+0903>)&nbsp;<U+2013> Hindi deliberation on ''R<U+0101>sapa<U+00F1>c<U+0101>dhy<U+0101>y<U+012B>''.
* (2006) ''Ahalyoddh<U+0101>ra'' (<U+0905><U+0939><U+0932><U+094D><U+092F><U+094B><U+0926><U+094D><U+0927><U+093E><U+0930>)&nbsp;<U+2013> Hindi discourse.
* (2008) ''Hara Te Bhe Hanum<U+0101>na'' (<U+0939><U+0930> <U+0924><U+0947> <U+092D><U+0947> <U+0939><U+0928><U+0941><U+092E><U+093E><U+0928>)&nbsp;<U+2013> Hindi discourse.

